videos.description: Isaiah Washington creates separation then nails a jumper in his defender's face.
videos.headline: Washington loses defender then nails a jumper

videos.description: Minnesota's ball movement leads to a two-handed Jordan Murphy slam.
videos.headline: Murphy uses nice footwork and then jams it

videos.description: Minnesota's Amir Coffey gets crafty around the rim with a neat reverse layup around an Iowa defender.
videos.headline: Coffey takes baseline for a beautiful finish around the rim

videos.description: Dupree McBrayer leads Minnesota's fast break, then tosses it up for Amir Coffey for a big throwdown.
videos.headline: Minnesota's fast break ends with Coffey slamming an alley-oop

videos.description: Dupree McBrayer comes away with a steal and hangs it up for Amir Coffey to flush home.
videos.headline: McBrayer lobs it up for Coffey

videos.description: Isaiah Moss gets a steal and goes all the way to the basket for a tough layup in traffic for Iowa.
videos.headline: Moss attacks the rim on fast break

videos.description: Dupree McBrayer throws it out to Eric Curry for a wide-open dunk to extend Minnesota's lead over Iowa.
videos.headline: Curry seals the game with fast-break slam
